The pinnacle of ultra-fine light control - Quantum Matrix Technology
The evolution of Neo QLED features Quantum Matrix technology, which precisely controls the exclusive new Quantum Mini LED.  Thanks to precise light control, you can enjoy great detail even in the darkest and brightest scenes. 
AI-based 8K image supplemented with 20 neural networks - Neural Quantum Processor 8K
Neo QLED's advanced multi-intelligent processor provides the best 8K viewing experience.  To analyze visual data, instead of a single neural network, Neo Quantum Processor 8K uses data generated by 20 neural networks to enhance every visual detail of 8K content
Absolute beauty in minimalism - Infinity One design
Don't make a compromise between elegance and a captivating visual experience!  This beautiful Infinity One design takes it to the next level with an incredibly thin profile. 
Dolby Atmos experience with high-end speakers - Dolby Atmos® 
Samsung's new high-end speakers provide a new level of Dolby Atmos experience, immersing players in the action with multi-dimensional sound. 
Exceptional motion enhancement at 4K 120Hz - Motion Xcelerator Turbo+
Defeat all enemies, even at soaring speeds!  Thanks to the exceptional motion enhancement of up to 4K 120 Hz, you can enjoy the gameplay with extremely smooth action, without delay or motion blur. 
Smooth, stutter-free, low-latency HDR gaming - FreeSync Premium Pro
Reduced stuttering and screen tearing thanks to the certified AMD FreeSync Premium Pro™ core technology and the excellent combination of high-performance, smooth gameplay, exceptional high-dynamic-range visuals and low latency provide the performance you need to truly win games. 
Dynamic, realistic sound that follows the action - Motion Tracking Sound+ (OTS+)
Thanks to the built-in speakers, you can enjoy vividly realistic 3D sound that puts you right in the middle of the action. 
Add beauty to the mess-free solution!  - Pluggable slim One Connect
Whatever the installation environment, the pluggable One Connect helps minimize cable clutter. 
Discover your favorite content in one place!  - Smart Hub
Samsung's new Smart Hub prioritizes content curation and discovery, so you can spend less time searching and more time streaming the movies, shows and other content you love. 
Video calls on the big screen - Video call app
Connect seamlessly with your loved ones on the bigger screen with Google Duo.  Using the Samsung Slim Fit Cam or your own smartphone's camera, you can make video calls much easier. 
Your best home butler - SmartThings
Relax and let your intelligent butler do the rest!  SmartThings can seamlessly connect, monitor and control all your smart devices and intuitively control your home.  You can control the devices directly with a remote control or voice while watching TV. 
You can see everything on one screen - Multi View
Watch TV and mobile phone simultaneously on the same screen.  Whether it's live sports statistics or referee video, simply connect your phone and you can watch it on more screens than ever before.
